# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
So using Sliding Window These are the steps:

- Insert one by one in map and also check a condition along with this .
- Condition is if mp[s[i]] is >1 i.e is a duplicate so remove it .
- Keep a maxi varaible for maximum window size.
# Complexity
- Time complexity:O(n)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity:O(128) --> can be taken as constant or surely less than using a map direclty
